title: 17 Things COD: Modern Warfare 2 Players Discovered So Far

media:group.media:title: 17 Things COD: Modern Warfare 2 Players Discovered So Far
media:group.media:description: From cheesing XP to level quickly, to the new slide cancel, and finding strange places to hang off of, the Modern Warfare 2 community has been hard at work testing multiplayer while waiting for Warzone 2.0. Here’s what you’ve found so far.
